                            <comment id="14039931" author="tilman" created="Sat, 21 Jun 2014 19:31:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in the 1.8 branch rev 1604450 for axial and radial shading.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14040086" author="tilman" created="Sun, 22 Jun 2014 09:48:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached file pattern-shading-2-4-noMatrix.pdf is the same as  pattern-shading-2-4-idMatrix.pdf from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2141&quot; title=&quot;Shading not applied to text&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2141&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2141&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, except that I blanked the identity matrices in the PDF files with a hex editor. The problem with the not / badly shaded text will be handled there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14040090" author="tilman" created="Sun, 22 Jun 2014 09:54:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in rev 1604555 in the 2.0 version for shading types 4 and 5.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
